ipconfig /renew

tracert 141.1.1.1

ping 141.1.1.1



#####################################################
WGET on windows git bash:
#########################
- download: https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/?source=typ_redirect
- unpack
- create ~/bin directory
- move wget.exe to ~/bin
- now you are able to run wget from your windows git bash command line


################################
problems being able getting pinged?
Make sure that the Firewall rule "File and Printer Sharing (Echo Request - ICMPv4-In)" is enabled.
Without that all ping reuests will be ignored.


################################
Computer Name?
In order to find out your computer name you can use nslookup:
$ nslookup 10.100.102.43
Server:  dc-vm.rz.company.de
Address:  10.100.38.50

Name:    sto-clei.rz.company.de
Address:  10.100.102.43
